F4HWN Edition Fusion firmware for Quansheng UV-K1 and UV-K5 V3
================================================================

This product includes software originally developed by Dual Tachyon
for the Quansheng UV-K5 open-source firmware project:

  https://github.com/DualTachyon/uv-k5-firmware

This product includes work derived from Egzumer's UV-K5 custom
firmware:

  https://github.com/egzumer/uv-k5-firmware-custom

This product includes work developed by Armel / F4HWN and contributors
for the F4HWN firmware projects, including the F4HWN Edition Fusion
port for UV-K1 and UV-K5 V3 radios:

  https://github.com/armel/uv-k5-firmware-custom
  https://github.com/armel/uv-k1-k5v3-firmware-custom

The UV-K1 and UV-K5 V3 port is the result of joint work by muzkr and
Armel / F4HWN.

